summary:
Tilburg based Agronomist Engineer, with years of experience in Quality of a wide variety of fruits and vegetables at arrival, stock control and quality after repacking, being my main expertise related to Blueberries. 

My education and work experience makes the perfect match in the world of Fruit and Vegetables, especially when it is necessary to have a  technical link between the producer and the importer/buyer.

I'm looking for a challenge as a Quality Inspector in a company that is looking for a motivated person with humor and who is not afraid to give her opinion. I'm easy going with people at all levels, clear, independent with good social and communication skills, able to work independently as well as in a team, carrying out my work accurately and purposefully.
